section 7.content:
\label{ablation_ontology_encoder}
In this section, we report the results of ablation studies on the property guided triple scoring and the neighborhood aggregation in the disentangled ontology encoder when incorporating with GCN-based methods.
The results are shown in Table~\ref{tab:ablation_ontology_encoder_pro}.

